t.com/wp-dyn/content/gallery/2010/07/23/GA2010072306017.html|title=Gen. McChrystal's retirement ceremony marked by laughter, regret|publisher=Washingtonpost.com|date=2010-07-23|accessdate=2012-11-12|archive-date=2018-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181027163055/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/gallery/2010/07/23/GA2010072306017.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==退役后工作==
2010年后离开军队，麦克里斯特尔进入了[[耶鲁大学|耶鲁大学]][[杰克逊全球事务研究所|杰克逊全球事务研究所]]担任高级研究员，教授题为“领导力”的课程。该课程是一项主要面向研究生的讲座，也为本科生预留一些位子，课程仅有20个位子，但2011年的申请量达到250人，2013年课程讲授了三次。<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2010/08/16/us/politics/AP-US-McChrystal-Retirement.html "McChrystal to Teach Course at Yale"], nytimes.com, August 16, 2010; accessed September 18, 2014.</ref><ref>Jane Darby Menton, [http://yaledailynews.com/crosscampus/2012/11/02/applications-for-mcchrystal-seminar-open "Applications for McChrystal seminar open"] {{Wayback|url=http://yaledailynews.com/crosscampus/2012/11/02/applications-for-mcchrystal-seminar-open |date=20130531100717 }}, yaledailynews.com, November 2, 2012; accessed September 18, 2014.</ref><ref name="huffingtonpost1">Ryan Grim, [http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/05/16/stanley-mcchrystal-lobbyist_n_862500.html Stanley McChrystal: Lobby Shop Working With Former General"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/05/16/stanley-mcchrystal-lobbyist_n_862500.html |date=20181027163606 }}, huffingtonpost.com, May 16, 2011; accessed September 18, 2014.</ref>

2010年11月，[[捷蓝航空|捷蓝航空]]宣布麦克里斯特尔将加入其董事会。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.theage.com.au/breaking-news-world/fired-mcchrystal-to-join-airline-board-20101110-17mmc.html|title=Fired McChrystal to join airline board|publisher=News.theage.com.au|date=2010-11-10|accessdate=2012-11-12|location=Melbourne|archive-date=2014-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102051600/http://news.theage.com.au/breaking-news-world/fired-mcchrystal-to-join-airline-board-20101110-17mmc.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2011年2月16日，[[航星国际|航星国际]]宣布麦克里斯特尔将加入其董事会。<ref>[http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-16/ret-gen-stanley-mcchrystal-joins-navistar-board.html "Ret. Gen. Stanley McChrystal joins Navistar board"], bloomberg.com, February 16, 2011; accessed September 18, 2014.</ref>


麦克里斯特尔是西门子政府系统董事会主席，是国际知识战略顾问委员会成员，一家与阿联酋非常密切的经销执照武器的公司。<ref name='DN_2012-12-13'>{{cite news|first=Aram|last=Roston|title=McChrystal Working for UAE-Owned Arms Brokerage|date=2012-12-13|publisher=[[Gannett_Government_Media|Gannett Government Media]]|url=http://www.defensenews.com/article/20121213/C4ISR01/312130004/McChrystal-Working-UAE-Owned-Arms-Brokerage|work=[[Defense_News|Defense News]]|accessdate=2012-12-13|archive-date=2013-01-21|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130121210107/http://www.defensenews.com/article/20121213/C4ISR01/312130004/McChrystal-Working-UAE-Owned-Arms-Brokerage|dead-url=yes}}</ref>他共同创立了麦克里斯特尔集团有限责任公司，一家位于[[亚历山德里亚_(弗吉尼亚州)|弗吉尼亚州亚历山德里亚]]的管理咨询公司。<ref name="rollcall.com">Kate Ackley, [http://www.rollcall.com/news/-202945-1.html "McChrystal's New Consulting Firm Taps Hill Aides"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rollcall.com/news/-202945-1.html |date=20181027163138 }}, rollcall.com, January 29, 2011; accessed September 18, 2014.</ref><ref>Kate Ackley, [http://www.rollcall.com/news/former_appropriations_aides_launch_new_lobby_shop-205598-1.html "Former Appropriations Aides Launch New Lobby Shop"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rollcall.com/news/former_appropriations_aides_launch_new_lobby_shop-205598-1.html |date=20181027163151 }}, rollcall.com, May 13, 2011; accessed September 18, 2014.</ref>他的领导和组织建设思想是[[丹尼尔·列维京|丹尼尔·列维京]]和他的畅销书[[有条不紊的思路|有条不紊的思路]]常引用的。

